.SH STANDARDS
.B shelf
is a generic ELF generation engine. The specific standards and ABI
compliance are determined by the chosen \fBplan\fR file.
.PP
Plans under the \fBamd64/linux/\fR directory target the \fBELF-64\fR
format as defined in the \fBSystem V ABI\fR for \fBamd64\fR. These
plans utilize \fBELFDATA2LSB\fR (little-endian) encoding and
\fBEM_X86_64\fR machine types.
